name: Hullmod installer
desc: A hull alteration is a special, consumable hull modification that can be installed through the "Additional Options" section at the top of the refit screen.

name: Gravitational Destabilizer
desc:
A device that discharges a small pellet of antimatter at intense gravitational pressure. Activating it creates a rift in hyperspace.

Integrating it into your fleet unlocks access to the "Singularity Jump" ability.

name: Artifact
desc: An ancient device that can be integrated into a fleet to provide additional benefits. Only one can be active at a time. More information will be provided via the "Artifacts" intel tab (located in the "Personal" section) when integrating for the first time.
